'''Berk''' is a [[slang]] term derived from [[cockney rhyming slang]]. It is a shortened version of [[Berkeley Hunt]], the [[hunting with hounds|hunt]] based at [[Berkeley Castle]] in [[Gloucestershire]], in the [[UK]].  In the rhyming slang, "hunt" is made to rhyme with [[cunt]] giving the word berk it's slang meaning.  It is not perceived to be excessively rude, perhaps because whilst it is known for being a slang word, it's real meaning is not well known.

